	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Can PC10 games run @ 50 hz ?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />No, the PlayChoice-10 implies a 2C03 PPU, which can only operate at 60 Hz.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


